title: High
overview: "Magic", the drug that has everyone hooked to it since the day it has been made available on the streets. The makers, the users, the doctors, the pharmaceutical company which is involved in it, a news reporter, a local gangster, a detective and a drug user himself, all are revolving around this drug. With so much black money flowing in, so many people hooked to it and so many people after the truth of this, who will reach the end of their success journey?
